    border-radius: 1;
	background-color: #ccc;
}
```
Then add this CSS later:
```css
.something Button {
    border-radius: 0;
}
```

**To Reproduce**
https://play.nativescript.org/?template=play-js&id=vjUfza&v=2

**Expected behavior**
The ripple to be restored

